Package: spinifex
Title: Manual controls for manipulating dimensions in high-dim (p>3) Spaces
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Nicholas", "Spyrison", email = "spyrison@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Dianne", "Cook", role = c("aut", "ths"))
    )
Description: Used in touring; orthagonal linear projections of numeric 
  multivariate data (p>3). Implements manual tours, for manipulation of single 
  variables. Additionally offers graphic output as gganimate and plotly 
  including tourr tour paths.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.4.0),
    tourr
License: GPL-3
BugReports: https://github.com/nspyrison/spinifex/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
